your life will be forfeit.

1676
02:47:22,166 --> 02:47:23,701
Then it is forfeit.

1677
02:47:26,304 --> 02:47:28,339
Release them.

1678
02:47:38,582 --> 02:47:44,122
Sauron's wrath will be terrible,
his retribution swift.

1679
02:47:45,956 --> 02:47:48,526
[RUMBLING]

1680
