will ever say:

1687
02:48:21,091 --> 02:48:23,494
"Let's hear about Frodo
and the Ring."

1688
02:48:23,494 --> 02:48:26,830
And they'll say, "Yes! That's
one of my favorite stories."

1689
02:48:26,830 --> 02:48:30,100
